name: googoosh - tribute گــــوگـــوش
description:
Faegheh Atashin - گوگوش currently has an estimated net worth of 60-70 million dollars. like shirly temple, she was raised as a performer from a very young age and earned international fame with her movies and music performances. 
after the iranian revolution of 1979, for 21 years she did not perform and remained silent in iran. on 29 July 2000, with an audience of more than 12,000, she sang to sold-out concert in toronto, canada. her elegant style and beautiful voice continues to win over audiences today.
